        DataDetailDescription:"The shoot for Diljit Dosanjh and Kriti Sanon's film 'Arjun Patiala' began in February this year. The film is backed by Bhushan Kumar and Dinesh Vijan. Helmed by Rohit Jugraj, the film also stars Varun Sharma. Diljit will be seen as a cop while Kriti is playing a character of a crime reporter in the film. The comedy film was supposed to hit the theatres on September 18, however, things didn't go as planned. Now, the film has finally got a release date. Kriti shared the news on her social media. The film will be hitting the screens on May 3, 2019. Sharing the poster, she captioned the image,Ready. Steady. LOL. #ArjunPariala to hit the screens on May 3, 2019.",
